Package: scONCO
Title: Hierarchical, AI-Augmented Marker-Based Annotation for Cancer Single-Cell Transcriptomics
Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2026-05-26
Authors@R: c(
    person("Chia-Jung", "Chang",
